ia_8b4f8d78ca15":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md"],"id":"obs_mqvrrkia_8b4f8d78ca15","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md\",\"new_string\":\"- Admin can open a new engagement for any client for any tax year (manual, one per client per year).\\n- Admin can transition an engagement to any status from any status (bidirectional).\\n- Every status transition is recorded in a `client_engagement_history` table (frÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md\",\"ÔÇª","timestamp":"2026-06-27T02:57:18.191Z","title":"Edit","type":"file_edit"},"obs_mqvrrsx3_a57fe3d1d699":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md"],"id":"obs_mqvrrsx3_a57fe3d1d699","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md\",\"new_string\":\"### US-3 ÔÇö Transition status\\nAs an admin, on a client's Workflow tab, I can change the status of any engagement using a dropdown or action button. I can optionally add a note before confirming. The change is saved immediately, recorded in the history, and triggers aÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md\",\"ÔÇª","timestamp":"2026-06-27T02:57:29.092Z","title":"Edit","type":"file_edit"},"obs_mqvrryoq_97853e873023":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md"],"id":"obs_mqvrryoq_97853e873023","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md\",\"new_string\":\"## Open Questions\\n\\n_All open questions resolved during requirements review._\",\"old_string\":\"## Open Questions\\n\\n- OQ-1: Should the workflow dashboard show only the **most recent** engagement per client, or allow showing all years (with a year filter)?\\n- OQ-2: WhaÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md\",\"ÔÇª","timestamp":"2026-06-27T02:57:36.568Z","title":"Edit","type":"file_edit"},"obs_mqvrs5xm_271fd5363765":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md"],"id":"obs_mqvrs5xm_271fd5363765","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md\",\"new_string\":\"## Data Model\\n\\n**Additions to `clients` table (V13 migration):**\\n```\\nbusiness_type            VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL   -- PERSONAL | CORPORATE | SELF_EMPLOYED\\nfiscal_year_end_month    SMALLINT NULL          -- 1ÔÇô12; NULL for PERSONAL (always 12)\\nfiscal_year_end_dÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/docs/superpowers/specs/2026-06-26-client-workflow-requirements.md\",\"ÔÇª","timestamp":"2026-06-27T02:57:45.961Z","title":"Edit","type":"file_edit"},"obs_mqvrsbi8_6b6cbcfeba63":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqvrsbi8_6b6cbcfeba63","importance":5,"narrative":"","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","timestamp":"2026-06-27T02:57:53.183Z","title":"subagent_stop","type":"subagent"},"obs_mqvrsdcx_d