","subtitle":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\",\"taskId\":\"1\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T02:59:09.847Z","title":"TaskUpdate","type":"file_edit"},"obs_mqvrueuo_13a186aa9923":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/proposal.md"],"id":"obs_mqvrueuo_13a186aa9923","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"content\":\"---\\nDate: 2026-06-26\\nChange: client-workflow\\nRequirements: requirements.md\\n---\\n\\n## Why\\n\\nThe firm currently has no structured way to track where each client's tax return stands in the annual filing cycle ÔÇö work state lives only in email threads and staff memory. Introducing a formal per-client, per-tax-year engagement workflow gives the admin a single source of truth for filingÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"content\":\"---\\nDate: 2026-06-26\\nChange: client-workflow\\nRequirements: requirements.md\\n---\\n\\n## Why\\n\\nThe firm cuÔÇª","timestamp":"2026-06-27T02:59:30.830Z","title":"Write","type":"file_write"},"obs_mqvruhzx_da6513408da6":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqvruhzx_da6513408da6","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"command\":\"openspec status --change client-workflow --json 2>&1\",\"description\":\"Check artifact status after writing proposal\"} | {\"interrupted\":false,\"isImage\":false,\"noOutputExpected\":false,\"stderr\":\"\",\"stdout\":\"{\\n  \\\"changeName\\\": \\\"client-workflow\\\",\\n  \\\"schemaName\\\": \\\"superpowers-driven\\\",\\n  \\\"isComplete\\\": false,\\n  \\\"applyRequires\\\": [\\n    \\\"tasks\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"artifacts\\\": [\\n    {\\n ÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"command\":\"openspec status --change client-workflow --json 2>&1\",\"description\":\"Check artifact status after writing prÔÇª","timestamp":"2026-06-27T02:59:34.906Z","title":"Bash","type":"command_run"},"obs_mqvrujgo_41d178c5ac3f":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"fa