:\"Fetch specs artifact instrÔÇª","timestamp":"2026-06-27T02:59:42.743Z","title":"Bash","type":"command_run"},"obs_mqvruvjk_2bdc1cc9c427":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqvruvjk_2bdc1cc9c427","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"command\":\"mkdir -p /Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-engagement-workflow && mkdir -p /Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/admin-workflow-ui && mkdir -p /Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-management\",\"description\":\"Create spec subdirectories\"} | {\"interrupted\":fÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"command\":\"mkdir -p /Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-engagement-workÔÇª","timestamp":"2026-06-27T02:59:52.463Z","title":"Bash","type":"command_run"},"obs_mqvrv5rx_0f670b6bcb1b":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-management/spec.md"],"id":"obs_mqvrv5rx_0f670b6bcb1b","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"content\":\"## ADDED Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: Client has a business type\\nEvery client record SHALL have a `business_type` field with one of three values: PERSONAL, CORPORATE, or SELF_EMPLOYED. The field is required on creation and may be updated by the admin.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Create client with valid business type\\n- **WHEN** an authenticated admin sends `POST /api/admin/clients` with `ÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"content\":\"## ADDED Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: Client has a business type\\nEvery client record SHALL have a `busÔÇª","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:00:05.723Z","title":"Write","type":"file_write"},"obs_mqvrvr9w_4bffd29702f1":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-engagement-workflow/spec.md"],"id":"obs_mqvrvr9w_4bffd29702f1","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"content\":\"## ADDED Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: Create a client engagement\\nThe system SHALL allow an authenticated admin to open a new engagement for a client for a specific tax year. Tax year is the calendar year in which the client's fiscal period ends. Only one engagement per client per tax year is permitted. A new engagement is created at status START.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Successful engaÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"content\":\"## ADDED Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: Create a client engagement\\nThe system SHALL allow an authenticatÔÇª","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:00:33.586Z","title":"Write","type":"file_write"},"obs_mqvrw8jv_00af123f953d":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/admin-workflow-ui/spec.md"],"id":"obs_mqvrw8jv_00af123f953d","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"content\":\"## ADDED Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: Admin workflow dashboard page\\nThe system SHALL provide a `/admin/workflow` page accessible only to authenticated admins. The page SHALL display a table of all client engagements across all tax years. Table columns: Client Name, Business Type, Tax Year, Status, Last Updated, Last Updated By. The table SHALL support filtering by Status and by BÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"content\":\"## ADDED Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: Admin workflow dashboard page\\nThe system SHALL provide a `/adminÔÇª","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:00:55.976Z","title":"Write","type":"file_write"},"obs_mqvrwdfi_6a93e8f029b1":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqvrwdfi_6a93e8f029b1","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"command\":\"openspec status --change client-workflow --json 2>&1\",\"description\":\"Check artifact status after writing specs\"} | 