e: 2026-06-26\\nChange: client-workflow\\nStatus: REVIEWED\\n---\\n\\n## Goals\\n\\n- Add a structured tax engagement workflow to the accounting firm app so that admins can track each client's filing progress per tax year.\\n- \\\"Tax year\\\" is defined as the year the fiscal pÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/requirements.md\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:11.565Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqvsfvej_45ccce6501e0":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/proposal.md"],"id":"obs_mqvsfvej_45ccce6501e0","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/proposal.md\"} | {\"file\":{\"content\":\"---\\nDate: 2026-06-26\\nChange: client-workflow\\nRequirements: requirements.md\\n---\\n\\n## Why\\n\\nThe firm currently has no structured way to track where each client's tax return stands in the annual filing cycle ÔÇö work state lives only in email threads and staff memory. IntroduciÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/proposal.md\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:12.057Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqvsfxsr_30eab2e34985":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md"],"id":"obs_mqvsfxsr_30eab2e34985","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md\"} | {\"type\":\"text\",\"file\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md\",\"content\":\"## Context\\n\\nThe app currently tracks clients as flat records (name, email, phone, admin ownership). There is no concept of a tax engagement lifecycle ÔÇö filing status existsÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:15.158Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqvsfxu3_7affb7bdd68b":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-management/spec.md"],"id":"obs_mqvsfxu3_7affb7bdd68b","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-management/spec.md\"} | {\"file\":{\"content\":\"## ADDED Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: Client has a business type\\nEvery client record SHALL have a `business_type` field with one of three values: PERSONAL, CORPORATE, or SELF_EMPLOYED. The field is required on creation and may be updated by the admin.\\n\\ÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-management/spec.md\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:15.206Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqvsg004_cecb48da612e":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-engagement-workflow/spec.md"],"id":"obs_mqvsg004_cecb48da612e","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-engagement-workflow/spec.md\"} | {\"file\":{\"content\":\"## ADDED Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: Create a client engagement\\nThe system SHALL allow an authenticated admin to open a new engagement for a client for a specific tax year. Tax year is the calendar year in which the client's fiscal period ends.ÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/