e":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01FRrhHamEZukPK44T3zGEAm\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:49:03.400Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwsvvhk_cb2a029a48fc":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-engagement-workflow/spec.md"],"id":"obs_mqwsvvhk_cb2a029a48fc","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-engagement-workflow/spec.md\"}","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-engagement-workflow/spÔÇª","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:49:05.797Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqwsvvhk_a8f558946d17":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvvhk_a8f558946d17","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_0128nvPuzxL27djwUZgmosuC\"} | 1\t## ADDED Requirements\n2\t\n3\t### Requirement: Create a client engagement\n4\tThe system SHALL allow an authenticated admin to open a new engagement for a client for a specific tax year. Tax year is the calendar year in which the client's fiscal period ends. Only one engagement per client per tax year is permitted. A new engagement is created at statuÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_0128nvPuzxL27djwUZgmosuC\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:49:05.991Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwsvvhk_a509ad54ae9c":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md"],"id":"obs_mqwsvvhk_a509ad54ae9c","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md\"}","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:49:06.323Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqwsvvhk_d3906de2f23e":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvvhk_d3906de2f23e","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_016dYNzDRMvQXVA5YU4BzESQ\"} | 1\t## Context\n2\t\n3\tThe app currently tracks clients as flat records (name, email, phone, admin ownership). There is no concept of a tax engagement lifecycle ÔÇö filing status exists only in staff email threads. This design introduces a `ClientEngagement` entity (one per client per tax year) with a five-state machine and a full transition audit trail, ÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_016dYNzDRMvQXVA5YU4BzESQ\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:49:06.498Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwsvvhk_c957f04f53ac":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvvhk_c957f04f53ac","importance":5,"narrative":"","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:49:11.219Z","title":"stop","type":"other"},"obs_mqwsvvhk_97bffb4f482a":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvvhk_97bffb4f482a","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"description\":\"2.E EVAL ÔÇö group 2 evaluator (haiku)\",\"model\":\"haiku\",\"prompt\":\"You are an external evaluator with a skeptical lens. You have no knowledge of the implementation decisions made during this session. Evaluate group 2 (ClientEngagement backend) of the client-workflow OpenSpec change.\\n\\n## Contract (group-2.md)\\n\\n```\\n### Contract\\n\\n- **Spec**: (client-engagement-workflow) \\\"The sysÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"description\":\"2.E EVAL ÔÇö group 2 evaluator (haiku)\",\"model\":\"haiku\",\"prompt\":\"You are an external evaluator with a skÔÇª","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:50:09.114Z","title":"Agent","type":"subagent"},"obs_mqwsvvhk_8fea4056d636":{"concepts