","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkgcr_c439e914d731":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/admin-workflow-ui/spec.md"],"id":"obs_mqwtkgcr_c439e914d731","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/admin-workflow-ui/spec.md\"}","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/admin-workflow-ui/spec.md\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T12:20:33.179Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqwtkgcr_c5886e51ad08":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md"],"id":"obs_mqwtkgcr_c5886e51ad08","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md\"}","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T12:20:33.244Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqwtkgcr_22e9a34f8b05":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgcr_22e9a34f8b05","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01A3Lr9XxuEFrGqUsqrvLLfU\"} | 1\t## ADDED Requirements\n2\t\n3\t### Requirement: Admin workflow dashboard page\n4\tThe system SHALL provide a `/admin/workflow` page accessible only to authenticated admins. The page SHALL display a table of all client engagements across all tax years. Table columns: Client Name, Business Type, Tax Year, Status, Last Updated, Last Updated By. The table ÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01A3Lr9XxuEFrGqUsqrvLLfU\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T12:20:33.334Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkgcr_fa5c3b2b17bf":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgcr_fa5c3b2b17bf","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01JnRx2LQhJQzJMmTQjGnAoa\"} | 1\t## Context\n2\t\n3\tThe app currently tracks clients as flat records (name, email, phone, admin ownership). There is no concept of a tax engagement lifecycle ÔÇö filing status exists only in staff email threads. This design introduces a `ClientEngagement` entity (one per client per tax year) with a five-state machine and a full transition audit trail, ÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01JnRx2LQhJQzJMmTQjGnAoa\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T12:20:33.404Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkgcr_4b69bb202802":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgcr_4b69bb202802","importance":5,"narrative":"","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","timestamp":"2026-06-27T12:20:35.080Z","title":"stop","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkgcr_d425e25568a4":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgcr_d425e25568a4","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"skill\":\"superpowers:requesting-code-review\",\"args\":\"--effort medium\"}","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"skill\":\"superpowers:requesting-code-review\",\"args\":\"--effort medium\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T12:20:35.735Z","title":"Skill","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkgcr_484bcc9f0e25":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgcr_484bcc9f0e25","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01Tyrx2uegZf2Psf9Dwcz7TB\"} | Launching skill: superpowers:requesting-code-review","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01Tyrx2uegZf2Psf9Dwcz7TB\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T12:20:35.871Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkgcr_b4f2b342b4e2":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgcr_b4f2b342b4e2"