,"timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:11.423Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqwtkge3_7c9c868145aa":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_7c9c868145aa","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_016qaJ9h9HK19gkH9wghaDn5\"} | 1\t---\n2\tDate: 2026-06-26\n3\tChange: client-workflow\n4\tStatus: REVIEWED\n5\t---\n6\t\n7\t## Goals\n8\t\n9\t- Add a structured tax engagement workflow to the accounting firm app so that admins can track each client's filing progress per tax year.\n10\t- \"Tax year\" is defined as the year the fiscal period **ends** (e.g., a Dec 31 personal client's 2024 engagement ÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_016qaJ9h9HK19gkH9wghaDn5\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:11.618Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkge3_541ee3f45b0e":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/proposal.md"],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_541ee3f45b0e","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/proposal.md\"}","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/proposal.md\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:11.939Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqwtkge3_8f95c626a635":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md"],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_8f95c626a635","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md\"}","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:15.011Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqwtkge3_e8316e2f3fe9":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_e8316e2f3fe9","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_016sNoDihhtLtNqJourRtHpA\"} | 1\t---\n2\tDate: 2026-06-26\n3\tChange: client-workflow\n4\tRequirements: requirements.md\n5\t---\n6\t\n7\t## Why\n8\t\n9\tThe firm currently has no structured way to track where each client's tax return stands in the annual filing cycle ÔÇö work state lives only in email threads and staff memory. Introducing a formal per-client, per-tax-year engagement workflow giveÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_016sNoDihhtLtNqJourRtHpA\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:12.108Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkge3_87c8edd7167e":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-management/spec.md"],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_87c8edd7167e","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-management/spec.md\"}","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-management/spec.md\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:15.094Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqwtkge3_2d52fef562fd":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_2d52fef562fd","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01QedeRxymBdndbkfWGzMgq1\"} | 1\t## Context\n2\t\n3\tThe app currently tracks clients as flat records (name, email, phone, admin ownership). There is no concept of a tax engagement lifecycle ÔÇö filing status exists only in staff email threads. This design introduces a `ClientEngagement` entity (one per client per tax year) with a five-state machine and a full transition audit trail, ÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01QedeRxymBdndbkfWGzMgq1\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:15.214Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkge3_2d47ca6bd16b":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_2d47ca6bd16b","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01EAY6NtWBZPBT8M1VLQmwm6\"} | 1\t## ADDED Requirements\n2\t\n3\t### Requirement: Client has a business type\n4\tEvery client record SHALL have a `business_type` field with one of three values: PERSONAL, CORPORATE, or SELF_EMPLOYED. The field is required on creation and may be updated by the admin.\n5\t\n6\t#### Scenario: Create client with valid business type\n7\t- **WHEN** an authenticatedÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01EAY6NtWBZPBT8M1VLQmwm6\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:15.259Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkge3_2d80aa2aaa76":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-engagement-workflow/spec.md"],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_2d80aa2aaa76","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-engagement-workflow/spec.md\"}","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/client-engagement-workflow/spÔÇª","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:17.867Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqwtkge3_5075c920e49e":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/admin-workflow-ui/spec.md"],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_5075c920e49e","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/admin-workflow-ui/spec.md\"}","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/specs/admin-workflow-ui/spec.md\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:18.486Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqwtkge3_d9dcb8b7d83a":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_d9dcb8b7d83a","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01D94kSCiT2PnrrUiis8bSMK\"} | 1\t## ADDED Requirements\n2\t\n3\t### Requirement: Create a client engagement\n4\tThe system SHALL allow an authenticated admin to open a new engagement for a client for a specific tax year. Tax year is the calendar year in which the client's fiscal period ends. Only one engagement per client per tax year is permitted. A new engagement is created at statuÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01D94kSCiT2PnrrUiis8bSMK\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:18.069Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkge3_b1b3ed34f01e":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_b1b3ed34f01e","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01UDeb9GsWLkcU9et6tsW7dE\"} | 1\t## ADDED Requirements\n2\t\n3\t### Requirement: Admin workflow dashboard page\n4\tThe system SHALL provide a `/admin/workflow` page accessible only to authenticated admins. The page SHALL display a table of all client engagements across all tax years. Table columns: Client Name, Business Type, Tax Year, Status, Last Updated, Last Updated By. The table ÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01UDeb9GsWLkcU9et6tsW7dE\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:18.664Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkge3_a21eacb50be9":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_a21eacb50be9","importance":5,"narrative":"","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:16:21.510Z","title":"stop","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkge3_72ea5f72e036":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"fi