","title":"stop","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkge3_283519b5719a":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md"],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_283519b5719a","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md\"}","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/client-workflow/design.md\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:38:01.772Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqwtkge3_220cbe299401":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_220cbe299401","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01DQUAHBcyNZEHitACrQt9s7\"} | 1\t## Context\n2\t\n3\tThe app currently tracks clients as flat records (name, email, phone, admin ownership). There is no concept of a tax engagement lifecycle ÔÇö filing status exists only in staff email threads. This design introduces a `ClientEngagement` entity (one per client per tax year) with a five-state machine and a full transition audit trail, ÔÇª","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01DQUAHBcyNZEHitACrQt9s7\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:38:01.940Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkge3_1b5a6bcf706c":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_1b5a6bcf706c","importance":5,"narrative":"","sessionId":"59998ae9-1dbf-4d8a-8963-1eef313b3a09","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:38:22.732Z","title":"stop","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkge3_14e93eb68937":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/backend/src/main/resources/db/migration/V14__create_client_engagements.sql"],"id":"obs_mqwtkge3_14e93eb68937","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/backend/src/main/resources/db/migration/V14__create_client_engagements.sql\"